Above the Law -LRB- also known as Nico -RRB- is a 1988 American action film written , produced and directed by Andrew Davis , and also produced by and starring Steven Seagal in his film debut .
The film co-stars Pam Grier , Sharon Stone , Daniel Faraldo and Henry Silva .
This came about after a successful screen test , financed by Michael Ovitz , leading to Seagal being offered a contract by Warner Bros. .
The film was set and filmed on location in Chicago .
The film was released in the United States on April 8 , 1988 .